{"tid":2390430,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老人家有糖尿病，飲食有咩要注意？","createTime":"2021-02-01T14:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T02:48:53.000Z","uid":126626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa208acf550913611bb48b49eb92b0d9bcf60cb","tid":2390430,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"想問吓咁多位巴打絲打，我姨媽有糖尿病，都幾嚴重，之後我想搬過去同佢一齊住。<br />\n<br />\n請問起居飲食有啲乜嘢要注意？有冇過來人可以教吓小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上網睇咗好多攻略，都想睇多啲過來人點講，尤其飲食方面有冇啲乜嘢，我可以幫到姨媽？<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒各位巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064f7d5452b5a1feb05dab4f8df31dbebaffd240","tid":2390430,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"戒食升糖高嘅嘢<br />\n少食多餐<br />\n清淡"},{"pid":"0a454550f814ba4b304f0f5b8269250f9edba70e","tid":2390430,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:20:54.000Z","msg":"煮野可以用代糖就用代糖<br />\n煮飯唔好食白飯，落啲紅米呀之類<br />\n上網睇下有咩升糖指數高嘅就盡量唔好食"},{"pid":"bd40748da2451dfa3cd554ed50eff8b3597b1b37","tid":2390430,"uid":303050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffa208acf550913611bb48b49eb92b0d9bcf60cb","tid":2390430,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"想問吓咁多位巴打絲打，我姨媽有糖尿病，都幾嚴重，之後我想搬過去同佢一齊住。<br />\n<br />\n請問起居飲食有啲乜嘢要注意？有冇過來人可以教吓小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上網睇咗好多攻略，都想睇多啲過來人點講，尤其飲食方面有冇啲乜嘢，我可以幫到姨媽？<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒各位巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"小心苦瓜之類會降血糖<br />\n糖尿病亦都會容易低血糖"},{"pid":"d20a39d8938453df07223bab694259b3c6ae299d","tid":2390430,"uid":132227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:35:05.000Z","msg":"打完胰島素記得食嘢<br />\n好多時打慣咗之後 <br />\n又因為啲唔知咩原因食少一餐半餐 就會低血糖<br />\n<br />\n食飯都係多菜少肉、少甜、均衡飲食嗰類嘢<br />\n<br />\n另外睇下依家去到咩程度，督手指驗血糖、打胰島素針既方法都要老人家/你學<br />\n<br />\n如果控制得好其實可以同一般人冇分別 <br />\n樓主可以樂觀啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d8653335832c90af27ad8ff193cbdff3d9ff6ad","tid":2390430,"uid":267918,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"064f7d5452b5a1feb05dab4f8df31dbebaffd240","tid":2390430,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"戒食升糖高嘅嘢<br />\n少食多餐<br />\n清淡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"小食多餐真係唔比胰臟休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實最好一日一餐或者168.斷食"},{"pid":"d7c243d3cfde4406bf3776b4fca9aaf9a895b8ca","tid":2390430,"uid":340192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"今時今日糖尿病都唔係咁大不了<br />\n大部份都係過緊正常生活 唔洗咁擔心"},{"pid":"9d1e02e7de297f8ae5ba91f86b6c69b29c1e9af4","tid":2390430,"uid":28031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7d8653335832c90af27ad8ff193cbdff3d9ff6ad","tid":2390430,"uid":267918,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"064f7d5452b5a1feb05dab4f8df31dbebaffd240","tid":2390430,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"戒食升糖高嘅嘢<br />\n少食多餐<br />\n清淡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"小食多餐真係唔比胰臟休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實最好一日一餐或者168.斷食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"屌你老母唔識就唔好出黎鳩噏弱智少陣啦 <br />\n打左insulin/食左降血糖藥唔食野會hypoglycaemia架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0419edc25cab0918f352f68bd8fbaf0b5edecce","tid":2390430,"uid":267918,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"9d1e02e7de297f8ae5ba91f86b6c69b29c1e9af4","tid":2390430,"uid":28031,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote